public class SplitGraph<V,E>
extends org.jgrapht.graph.SimpleGraph<SplitGraphVertex<V,E>,org.jgrapht.graph.DefaultWeightedEdge>

Takes a Graph G and generates an equal graph that has 1 additional vertice for each edge e in G. *----* turns into *--*--*

moritzfuchs
